## Remarks  
 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs>物件具有<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs.Context%2A>可以指派給長時間執行的屬性<xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext>中的處理常式<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceView.ContextCreating>事件。 如需詳細資訊，請參閱[物件內容生命週期管理 (EntityDataSource)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/67bc2486-112c-47c3-b23f-0297f7ac2160)。  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 下列範例示範建立<xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext>變數<xref:System.Web.UI.Page>物件和其指派<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs.Context%2A>屬性<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs>物件。  
  
```  
public partial class _Default : System.Web.UI.Page  
    {  
        AdventureWorksModel.AdventureWorksEntities objCtx =  
            new AdventureWorksModel.AdventureWorksEntities();  
  
        protected void EntityDataSource2_ContextCreating(object sender,   
            EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs e)  
        {  
            e.Context = objCtx;  
        }  
    }  
  
```

  
  
